            <span class="utterance" who="#silberbartG" start="1776.801" end="x">These times where we did not work, did not make us stronger, on the contrary, it made us weaker because the whole day long we were sent out into the cold, we only had a thin suit, like a pajama, a pair of wooden shoes, no socks, and so we stayed the whole long day in a small fenced area in front of the <a class="term" href="#vothG_block">block</a>. We were cold, some had frostbite, frost on the fingers, and sometimes that became infected, an abscess, and many died of it.</span>
